channel.title: Anyone Need a BaconBizConf Ticket?
channel.description:
I bought one at the early bird price, but probably won't be able to make it due to some last-minute things that have come up. Since the event is limited to 65 people and is currently sold out, I feel bad taking up a spot if there are people hoping to go!
(BaconBizConf is this Thursday and Friday, May 26-27 in Philadelphia.)
